tapi hama.

474
00:36:27,085 --> 00:36:28,169
Apa kau sudah gila?

475
00:36:28,419 --> 00:36:30,463
Kau benar-benar sudah gila!

476
00:36:31,464 --> 00:36:32,799
Kau seperti psikopat!

477
00:36:40,848 --> 00:36:42,016
Dasar wanita gila!

478
00:36:42,475 --> 00:36:44,394
Aku nyaris mati karena wanita itu!

479
00:36:45,228 --> 00:36:47,647
- Berhenti!
- Lepaskan aku!

480
00:36:47,730 --> 00:36:50,691
Jangan tangkap aku, tapi dia!
Tangkap wanita gila itu.

481
00:36:50,775 --> 00:36:52,318
- Pegang dengan erat.
- Lepaskan aku!

482
00:36:52,985 --> 00:36:55,029
Sudah kubilang, tangkap wanita gila itu!

483
00:36:55,113 --> 00:36:56,406
- Lepaskan!
- Diam!

484
00:37:06,707 --> 00:37:09,085
Apa pisaunya terluka?
Kenapa kau membalut pisaunya?

485
